
    # HIROSHI'S DAY 0


label hiro_D0_A:

    "I'm greeted by the sight of a… cute box? It's plastered in the theme of office stickers."

    "A briefcase, a little computer on a desk, and what seems to be a pile of papers with a pen."

    "Opening it, I chuckle when I see the adorable figurine inside. It looks so small."

    show sponsor_amused

    sponsor "You like him?"

    mc "I kind of do, actually."

    "I look around my apartment, and head over to the coffee table, sweeping the contents to the side and placing my figurine on it."

    "It's been a while since I've gotten a collectible, and it feels nice to be able to place something new there."

    sponsor "Well! Seems like he fits just right in."

    "Mystery Sponsor pulls out what seems like a card, and stamps over a tab. He hands it to me."

    show sponsor_happy

    "Make sure to keep this somewhere safe!"

    mc "What is this? And, does this mean I get to have more-"

    "Before I knew it, it had disappeared. Where has it gone?"

    mc "Mystery Sponsor?"

    "I stand to leave my living room in search of it. I trudge through piles and mountains of messes, and I groan."

    "You know it's rude to just appear and disappear without saying anything! Jeez…"

    "After a few minutes, I give up and return to my living room. The little box stays where it is, and I take the figurine out and look a little bit closer."

    menu:
        "Choose"
        "Comment on how cute the figurine is.":
            jump hiro_D0_AA
        "Examine the figurine by twirling it slowly.":
            jump hiro_D0_AB
        "\"Oops!\"":
            jump hiro_D0_AC

label hiro_D0_AA:

    mc "Aren't you a little cutie patootie?"

    "I grin while looking over the figurine. Somehow, I can see the pale skin grow a little red."

    "That's… interesting. Is it reactive?"

    mc "You're the cutest little thing I've seen in a while. You fit right in my collection, don't you?"

    "Unmistakably, the figurine's cheeks flush a tinge of pink. I raise an eyebrow."

    return

label hiro_D0_AB:

    "Being careful, I gently turn the toy around in my hand."

    "I see the details on it; the wrinkles on the shirt, the pair of round glasses, even the way the little beard stubble is designed."

    "I smile a bit."

    mc "I wonder what your name is. You must have one, right?"

    "I pick up the box once more and check all of its sides to try and find some sort of name tag, but to no avail."

    jump hiro_D0_B

label hiro_D0_AC:

    "My grip slips and I accidentally drop the toy face down to the ground."

    mc "Shit, sorry!"

    "I picked it up quickly, and noticed that the forehead turned… purple? Maybe it's an interactive toy? I feel so bad!"

    "I brush the seemingly bruised spot apologetically. I should really be more careful."

    jump hiro_D0_B

label hiro_D0_B:

    "I huff softly, looking back at the box now discarded on the floor. I pick it up and just settle it on the table."

    "Examining my figurine again, it seems to feel quite strange the more I hold on to it."

    "What the hell?"

    "I look around my messy apartment. Then quietly, I whisper."

    mc "Can you hear me?"

    "The figurine does not react. I mean, why would it? But something feels genuinely off. With another hesitant breath-"

    mc "What's your name?"

    "Nothing. I laugh, feeling silly. Why in the world would a figurine ever talk back to me anyway?"

    "I examine it a little closer. It's an adorable piece of work, if I'm honest. It feels like it was carved with a lot of love."

    mc "Where do you want to stay?"

    "I hold up the figurine, pretending to help it see through my apartment. I chuckle."

    mc "Sorry for the mess. But I'm sure I can put you somewhere you'd be displayed nicely."

    "I stand and decide to put him on the table near the dining room."

    "Brushing aside the paper bags, I wipe the messes and stains with my sleeve and carefully place the figurine there."

    mc "Here. How's that? I'm sure you won't need your box, anyway."

    "The figurine looks strangely out of place despite the way my other collectibles surround my house."

    "It's like he has a vibe of his own. And with the way it looks there, are his eyebrows actually furrowed..?"

    "I rub my eyes and blink a few times. I swear he had a different face a second ago."

    menu:
        "Choose"
        "Gently":
            jump hiro_D0_BA
        "Normally":
            jump hiro_D0_BB
        "Curiousity":
            jump hiro_D0_BC

label hiro_D0_BA:

    "With my other hand, I slowly reach over to the figurine's hand and pinch it between my fingers."

    "..."

    "Nothing."

    "I squeeze it a bit."

    "..."

    "The toy's face flushes red."

    mc "Huh."

    "I attempt to pinch its cheek."

    "It gets even redder."

    jump hiro_D0_C

label hiro_D0_BB:

    "I tilt my head to the side. With my other hand, I pat the figurine's head with my index finger."

    "His face becomes neutral instead of distressed. I squint to really try and see how his face shifted..."

    mc "Hm..."

    jump hiro_D0_C

label hiro_D0_BC:

    "Without really thinking. I shake the figurine for a few seconds."

    "..."

    "Its skin had turned into a slightly greenish hue. My eyebrows furrow."

    "I poke its nose."

    "..."

    "The expression shifted, seemingly more annoyed as I toyed with it."

    mc "Hm..."

    jump hiro_D0_C

label hiro_D0_C:

    "I huff quietly. Maybe it must really just be a very detailed, very interactable and unique collectible."

    "As much as I'd expect from such a strange creature."

    mc "Thanks, Mystery Sponsor... I guess?"

    "I return the figurine back on the table and notice the sun setting outside."

    "Sighing, I look over the toy one last time before retreating to my room."

    mc "Oh well."

    "I curl up in my bed quietly, the strange feeling still stirring in the pit of my stomach as I allow sleep to take over..."

    



